rows.label: qst005603_msg001
rows.name: Hello.

rows.label: qst005603_msg002
rows.name: What is it you want with me, mo?

rows.label: qst005603_msg003
rows.name:
We're researching an
ancient stone tablet...

rows.label: qst005603_msg004
rows.name: An ancient stone tablet, mo?

rows.label: qst005603_msg005
rows.name:
Yes, it's a transparent, thin
tablet that floats in the air.

rows.label: qst005603_msg006
rows.name: Well, that is a rare thing, mo.

rows.label: qst005603_msg007
rows.name:
I have indeed heard that in ancient times,
there was a technology to make letters
and pictures float in the air, mo.

rows.label: qst005603_msg008
rows.name:
Perhaps that tablet is part
of that technology, mo.

rows.label: qst005603_msg009
rows.name:
I heard you have an ancient
text about it. Is that true?

rows.label: qst005603_msg010
rows.name:
I do have an ancient text
from that era, mo...

rows.label: qst005603_msg011
rows.name:
It might have something written
about the tablet you mentioned, mo.

rows.label: qst005603_msg012
rows.name: Would you like to try reading it, mo?

rows.label: qst005603_msg013
rows.name: Really?!

rows.label: qst005603_msg014
rows.name:
Yes, you can try to
decipher it yourself, mo.

rows.label: qst005603_msg015
rows.name: How was it, Shiki?

rows.label: qst005603_msg016
rows.name:
It seems to be about
ancient technology, but...

rows.label: qst005603_msg017
rows.name:
There isn't much about that
tablet in particular...

rows.label: qst005603_msg018
rows.name: It seems to have a name, E46S, but...

rows.label: qst005603_msg019
rows.name: Hey, that E46S...

rows.label: qst005603_msg020
rows.name:
Oh! That's right, it must be
part of the twelve-digit code!

rows.label: qst005603_msg021
rows.name:
I wish we could figure it all
out at once, but it's good
that we're making progress.

rows.label: qst005603_msg022
rows.name: Yep, yep! It's all thanks to everyone.
